丁忧赋闲。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f8ea67c0f57f4d4b85aad8f0b09ab2c2\");'><span id='f8ea67c0f57f4d4b85aad8f0b09ab2c2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，19岁</div><div id='f8ea67c0f57f4d4b85aad8f0b09ab2c2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，游学杭州，时为学馆盛处。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ea0411906aba464ba0feec350fce62ce\");'><span id='ea0411906aba464ba0feec350fce62ce_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，47岁</div><div id='ea0411906aba464ba0feec350fce62ce' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年6月</a>，知临安府，复为徽猷阁待制，兼兵部侍郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，奏罢和买绢十万、铁三万、牛驴鹿皮二千。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏罢和买绢十万铁三万牛驴鹿皮二千。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，新城豪徐权出力捕杀群盗。盗有得逸者，妄诉其杀平民，几偿死。舜陟一问得情，诛盗而释豪，阖府称快。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7f8f2481fc244cad88efebeff8bcbc9a\");'><span id='7f8f2481fc244cad88efebeff8bcbc9a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1131')\">1131年</a>，48岁</div><div id='7f8f2481fc244cad88efebeff8bcbc9a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1131')\">1131年</a>，诏夺服乘驿赴行在，以故职宣谕京淮湖北，以秦桧之忌，谢归。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.899015,"Longitude":120.094566,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3305","Title":"湖州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"41a8ea5fbb1d4051b007d925631cd054\");'><span id='41a8ea5fbb1d4051b007d925631cd054_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，19岁</div><div id='41a8ea5fbb1d4051b007d925631cd054' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，游学湖州，时为学馆盛处。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"067f960dc6274658b257fc0f90d6dd2d\");'><span id='067f960dc6274658b257fc0f90d6dd2d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1140')\">1138-1140年</a>，55-57岁</div><div id='067f960dc6274658b257fc0f90d6dd2d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，丐祠居归安之射村，有词。<span class='label'>作品：</span>感皇恩词。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年3月27日</a>，命子仔采摭经传为之而序其谱。<span class='label'>作品：</span>孔子编年序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1139&endYear=1140')\">1139-1140年</a>，居归安。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.460864,"Longitude":117.950028,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3611","Title":"上饶","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7acb9e9b76b640cb86e06bae76015da2\");'><span id='7acb9e9b76b640cb86e06bae76015da2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，19岁</div><div id='7acb9e9b76b640cb86e06bae76015da2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，游学饶州，时为学馆盛处。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"420b1f243171456b8b19d4b9074c85db\");'><span id='420b1f243171456b8b19d4b9074c85db_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1109')\">1102-1109年</a>，19-26岁</div><div id='420b1f243171456b8b19d4b9074c85db' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1102&endYear=1102')\">1102年</a>，自饶徒步入京师，就补入学升内。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1103&endYear=1108')\">1103-1108年</a>，游太学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1109')\">1109年3月</a>，进士及第。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ee2474e5e8724b04b2ef7a26499a4989\");'><span id='ee2474e5e8724b04b2ef7a26499a4989_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1117')\">1111-1117年</a>，28-34岁</div><div id='ee2474e5e8724b04b2ef7a26499a4989' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1111')\">1111年</a>，赴调京师，馆于景德寺。夜，步月庭中，指月为对云：“圆少缺多天上月。”同赴调者应声戏云：“员多缺少部中官。”<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1112&endYear=1117')\">1112-1117年</a>，居京师？<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"958db33880dd41e4a89e2fb90687f1d4\");'><span id='958db33880dd41e4a89e2fb90687f1d4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1119&endYear=1123')\">1119-1123年</a>，36-40岁</div><div id='958db33880dd41e4a89e2fb90687f1d4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1119&endYear=1119')\">1119年</a>，改奉议郎睦亲宅宗子博士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1120')\">1120年</a>，居京师.<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1121&endYear=1121')\">1121年</a>，在京任御史台检法。冬，方腊乱，盗犯绩溪，家乡屋宇一夕煨烬，骨肉惊散，渡江逃避。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1122&endYear=1122')\">1122年</a>，居京师？<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1123')\">1123年</a>，在京为御史台检法。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1123')\">1123年</a>，在京任御察御史。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"02b429ee798342aea321a50c730fd10e\");'><span id='02b429ee798342aea321a50c730fd10e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1125&endYear=1127')\">1125-1127年</a>，42-44岁</div><div id='02b429ee798342aea321a50c730fd10e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1125&endYear=1125')\">1125年</a>，服阕再任监察御史。居京师。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年2月15日</a>，金人犯宋，中外多事，疏请依祖宗法许六察官言事，并极言军国利病，上许五日一对，大嘉奖之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞依祖宗法令监察御史言事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年2月19日</a>，奏论宇文虚中罪状及擅离任姓名。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论宇文虚中罪状及擅离任姓名。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年3月5日</a>，奏言攸罪不减乃父蔡京，当窜诸海岛。诏置万安军，寻遣使者随所至诛之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论蔡攸罪状。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年3月25日</a>，奏请褫郑修年亿年等职。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请褫郑修年亿年等职。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年3月25日</a>，上书言王孝迪之徒为社稷之贼，请斥之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏劾王孝迪。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年3月28日</a>，疏劾朱勔，上用其言，徙而斩之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾朱勔疏二篇。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年4月15日</a>，奏河北寇已遁去，而备御之计不可不讲，乞令大臣爱日，措画边备。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞措画边备疏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年4月16日</a>，再劾宇文虚中。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再劾宇文虚中。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年4月27日</a>，论其结成边患，乞戮之于市。时已窜柳州，诏即所至枭其首，徙妻子于万安军。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请诛赵良嗣。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年5月7日</a>，奏请责大臣以大义，使各安职业。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请责大臣以大义使各安职业。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年5月7日</a>，奏论宦官之害。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾李彀2篇。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年5月7日</a>，再劾蔡攸。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再劾蔡攸。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年5月25日</a>，奏閤门之职，祖宗所重，不可卖以求财，乞赐裁省诏閤门并立员额。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏乞裁省閤门员额。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年6月3日</a>，上疏请诏举文武官才堪将帅者。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请诏举文武官才堪将帅者。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，奏论台谏殿班先后。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论台谏殿班先后。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，奏请正是非及治道先后缓急之序。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请正是非及治道先后缓急之序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，进殿中侍御史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，奏通直郎秦元所著兵书阵图可用，诏令赐对。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏举秦元兵法可用。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年6月7日</a>，奏乞罢武臣提刑，以保甲属秦元，庶得专一从之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请罢武臣提刑以保甲属秦元专一训练。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，劾蔡懋凶悍，敢为不义，乞赐罢斥。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾蔡懋2篇。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年6月20日</a>，奏请夺赵野职郡。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请夺赵野职郡。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年6月26日</a>，奏请罢内侍领外局。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请罢内侍领外局。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年7月1日</a>，奏请慎密兵机。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请慎密兵机。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年7月28日</a>，奏请罢颜岐职事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请罢颜岐职事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年8月</a>，监秋试进士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，拜侍御史，面赐绯鱼，又赐文犀带。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年8月7日</a>，请东宫进讲仍旧制用孟子。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请诏东宫读孟子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年8月11日</a>，奏劾李偃。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏劾李偃。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年9月9日</a>，奏陈御戎策。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏陈御戎策。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月11日</a>，奏谯定究极象数，逆知人事，洞晓诸葛亮八阵法，宜厚礼招之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请厚礼招谯定。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月</a>，谏假金主尊号。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谏假金人名号。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月</a>，廷议遣康王使金，舜陟言肃王出质不反，当以为戒。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谏遣康王出使。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月23日</a>，河北重镇中山围急，疏乞救之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞救中山疏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月25日</a>，高丽入贡，至明州，舜陟奏言使者往往窥宋虚实以报金，请止勿朝，令本州递表入进。诏依。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞却高丽贡使。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月26日</a>，再疏乞救中山。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再乞救中山疏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年10月29日</a>，论金寇猖獗，由于天怒未解，宜修人事以应天。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论反正六事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年11月8日</a>，与臣僚合奏宋伯友多杀干和，使上皇负谤，请窜遐裔。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请罢黜宋伯友。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年11月17日</a>，金兵压境，上独召问曰：“卿尝以和议为不可信，今果然乎！将奈何？”对曰：“今日之策在于守河，大臣之议惟欲守城，则为失计。”退，陈备御之术，且言宰执得人则寇不足平。章下三省，宰执怒，拟下迁光禄。上不许。<span class='label'>作品：</span>金寇压境陈备御之术。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年11月18日</a>，以上所用唐恪、耿南仲、何囗、聂昌、李回皆非其人，因奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请择任人才并劾唐恪等。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年11月</a>，奏乞迁都。中书舍人孙觌以为忠臣之心而社稷万全之策也，亦上疏请纳。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏乞迁都。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年11月</a>，上以其言籍没谭稹财产。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年闰11</a>，金兵薄城下，唐恪从帝巡城，为都人遮击，策马得脱。舜陟劾其罪，因罢为中太一宫使。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再劾唐恪、聂昌。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年闰11</a>，金薄青城而军。舜陟言康王在河北，人服其忠义，乞多遣蜡书，以为元帅，募武勇来援。上乃遣秦仔等八人，以大元帅命王。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞命康王为元帅募兵来援。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年闰11</a>，金兵围城急，上方倚妖人郭京。舜陟力陈其不可。不用。京乃以六甲法尽令守御人下城，大启宣化门，出攻金人，大败。京托言下城作法，引余兵遁去。金兵登城，众皆披靡。京城陷。<span class='label'>作品：</span>上疏诋郭京不可用。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年</a>，治子城时，见都人喧闹，欲殴宦官，遂奏乞不差内侍上城，面奉从臣。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏乞不差内侍上城。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年1月6日</a>，奏论宦官之害。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论宦官之害。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年2月</a>，金人质天子邀金帛，梅执礼与同列陈知质、程振、安扶皆主根索不尽而见杀。舜陟奉诏督索，以言抗之，金酋怒，并舜陟及胡唐老、姚舜明、王坦等，各杖之百，几死是。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年4月4日</a>，金人立张邦昌为帝，称大楚。舜陟再上书请张邦昌退居臣位。<span class='label'>作品：</span>责张邦昌亟退位反正。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年4月</a>，请元祐皇后降诏诸路，使知中国有主，康王即位有日，以破乱臣贼子之心。<span class='label'>作品：</span>上疏元祐皇后请下诏播告天下。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年4月</a>，请留勤王兵邀还二圣。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请留勤王兵邀还二圣。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年4月20日</a>，上疏元祐皇后请迎康王。<span class='label'>作品：</span>上疏元祐皇后请迎康王。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年5月3日</a>，上疏议建四镇。未行。<span class='label'>作品：</span>上疏议建四镇。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b0e8f9d770c84822a99ec652c97ae1b0\");'><span id='b0e8f9d770c84822a99ec652c97ae1b0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1111')\">1109-1111年</a>，26-28岁</div><div id='b0e8f9d770c84822a99ec652c97ae1b0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1109')\">1109年3月</a>，授将仕郎越州山阴县簿会稽儒学教谕。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1110&endYear=1110')\">1110年6月2日</a>，次子仔生。妻汪氏为同邑敦礼坊汪藻公女，曾生长子亿，早卒，生年无考。汪氏历封沂国夫人。仔字元任，号苕溪渔隐，以荫补将仕郎，历官奉议郎，知晋陵县。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1111')\">1111年</a>，居越州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.750912,"Longitude":120.762045,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3304","Title":"嘉兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e0395fe33c4544c58b25983c9cc407d6\");'><span id='e0395fe33c4544c58b25983c9cc407d6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1117&endYear=1119')\">1117-1119年</a>，34-36岁</div><div id='e0395fe33c4544c58b25983c9cc407d6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1117&endYear=1117')\">1117年</a>，升通直郎秀州教授。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年7月27日</a>，三子传生。传字元辅，以荫补承务郎，历官至朝奉郎，知海宁县。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1119&endYear=1119')\">1119年</a>，居秀州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.017144,"Longitude":118.55143,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN320830","Title":"盱眙","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7a71f7d2e5024aff883059ad4e9c828b\");'><span id='7a71f7d2e5024aff883059ad4e9c828b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1125')\">1123-1125年</a>，40-42岁</div><div id='7a71f7d2e5024aff883059ad4e9c828b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1123')\">1123年4月20日</a>，阎太夫人卒，丁母忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1124&endYear=1125')\">1124-1125年</a>，居乡守制。<span class='label'>作品：</span>北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》）题秋香亭诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.82687,"Longitude":117.235447,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3401","Title":"合肥","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"012e3d9961a64e9596264bc21e243955\");'><span id='012e3d9961a64e9596264bc21e243955_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1129')\">1127-1129年</a>，44-46岁</div><div id='012e3d9961a64e9596264bc21e243955' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年</a>，转朝请郎秘阁修撰知庐州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年</a>，奏复帅府于庐州增筑东西水门纠合乡民为巡社。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏复帅府于庐州增筑东西水门纠合乡民为巡社。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年</a>，济南僧刘文舜聚党万余保舒州，投子山纵剽，舜陟遣介招降之，与高胜并命以官，以其徒为部曲，自是诸郡有警，檄之无不办。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年</a>，冀州云骑卒孙琦聚兵为盗，号一海虾，至庐，索赀粮，众请以粟遗之，舜陟乘城拒守不与，曰：“吾非有所爱，顾贼心无厌，与之则示弱，彼无能为也！”乃时出兵击其抄掠者。琦宵遁，命刘文舜将兵击之，斩获殆尽，得其辎重而归。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年11月</a>，丁进、李胜皆以巨盗合从，光、蕲、寿久被围。舜陟命刘文舜及其将破之，解三州之围。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年12月</a>，贼张遇自濠州奄至庐州属邑梁县，舜陟使人毁竹里桥，伏兵河西，伺其半渡击败之，斩首数千级，降兵万余，遇仅以身脱。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，知庐州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，知庐州，兼淮西安抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年9月</a>，丁进再寇淮西，遣刘文舜破之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，丁进攻光州，刘正彦受命讨进至庐，须兵，舜陟已先遣刘文舜破进，因拒正彦不与。正彦留屯不去，欲取庐州以自益，又不与。正彦不胜忿，闻于朝，舜陟亦劾其有异志。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾刘正彦。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年10月17日</a>，四子仰生。仰字元高，以荫补承务郎试中大法除大理评事，历官至朝议大夫直秘阁。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾刘正彦。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，叛将范琼破寿春焚掠，声摇淮浙，移书遣五骑责钱帛给军。叱斩其四，留一骑还报。又檄诸郡勿与粮。琼遂由光蕲绝江而南。时淮西八州，惟庐按堵。民绘其象于教弩台。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，加朝奉大夫集英殿修撰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年7月8日</a>，奏请身守江北之地以护行在。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请身守江北之地以护行在。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年7月8日</a>，除朝请大夫徽猷阁待制淮西制置使，入觐，抗言：“方今搢绅皆谓国势未易振，故兵备弛而土宇侵。自古未闻有颛务退避而能立国者，唯陛下坚意不屈，效汉高之必战，以起士心。”上嘉叹之。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2a9fba2b5e094ee99f2584ad53da0e10\");'><span id='2a9fba2b5e094ee99f2584ad53da0e10_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1134')\">1132-1134年</a>，49-51岁</div><div id='2a9fba2b5e094ee99f2584ad53da0e10' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年12月13日</a>，任庐寿等州宣抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年12月</a>，庐州残破，守者武人，责官逋在民者数万甚急，又托赡卒令市贩输金。至则蠲罢之。招集流散，官为筑室贷种，简集乡民威声甚震。伪齐豪帅王彦充遣其弟谷永求款附，将与之约，并力取刘豫，会议和乃止。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年</a>，为庐寿等州宣抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年2月24日</a>，改淮西安抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年3月7日</a>，王全犯庐州，至则降，复散财发粟，流民渐归。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年</a>，奏官包孝肃（包拯）曾孙。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏官包孝肃曾孙。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1134')\">1134年</a>，为淮西安抚使。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"901880c84ab5456d9ac9bf2142af2064\");'><span id='901880c84ab5456d9ac9bf2142af2064_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，46岁</div><div id='901880c84ab5456d9ac9bf2142af2064' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年闰81日</a>，改沿江都制置使、集英殿修撰，王羲叔副之，知建康府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，与右丞相杜充不相能。充时领兵驻建康，自遣将来夺取经制司钱物。舜陟闻于朝，充亦往往知而后奏。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5d43521e8c8547ab9b3436ed83848424\");'><span id='5d43521e8c8547ab9b3436ed83848424_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1130')\">1129-1130年</a>，46-47岁</div><div id='5d43521e8c8547ab9b3436ed83848424' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年9月24日</a>，朝廷知与杜充不合，移舜陟两浙宣抚司参谋。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，周望为两浙荆湖等路宣抚使，领兵守平江，舜陟为参谋官。望老缪，本由八行举，自枢府出为宣抚，与论军事率不合。先有旨令坚守平江，所措置初无可守之计，舜陟有奇谋皆不用。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，奏乞分兵前途控金虏，言者以争进为罪，降右文殿修撰。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年3月</a>，尝语望云：“枢密必欲守平江，莫若移军吴江，据太湖天险。吾辈以中军扼其前，使诸将以小舟自太湖旁击之，可必胜。”望不主其议，但令召诸将议之。及诸将毕集，望命舜陟语方略，诸将不从。盖诸将如郭仲威辈，皆贼魁，喜乱，志在为贼而已。陈思恭为统制，兵最少，居下，闻此谋，跃而前曰：“待制之言甚善！思恭愿为先锋。”自余不从，竟已。及金过吴江，舜陟遣禆将思恭以兵出太湖，横击其尾及中军，系虏之民闻兵至，皆为内应，纵火焚舟，几获四太子者。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.711328,"Longitude":116.007993,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3604","Title":"九江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9b838552806643d9938512e7f258bb31\");'><span id='9b838552806643d9938512e7f258bb31_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年</a>，49岁</div><div id='9b838552806643d9938512e7f258bb31' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年</a>，起复知江州兼沿江安抚使。时新经李成之祸，止存空垒，乃修城训兵。他日刘忠至城下，闻有备去。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年</a>，充京畿数路宣抚使。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":23.135308,"Longitude":113.270793,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4401","Title":"广州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"becd27af43fa47448c780e1dac451854\");'><span id='becd27af43fa47448c780e1dac451854_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1136')\">1134-1136年</a>，51-53岁</div><div id='becd27af43fa47448c780e1dac451854' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1134')\">1134年</a>，经略两广，征降贼将张广等，得兵五万余，兼平靖倭寇。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1135')\">1135年12月8日</a>，上疏乞罢保甲新法。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞罢保甲新法。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，知广州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.279893,"Longitude":110.296442,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4503","Title":"桂林","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1ea428b41f434be9b7b43f977d766e19\");'><span id='1ea428b41f434be9b7b43f977d766e19_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，53岁</div><div id='1ea428b41f434be9b7b43f977d766e19' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，除徽猷阁学士知静江府兼广西经略安抚使。听讼率尽辰漏，庭中肃然。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，知静江府。海寇周聪及东寇陈旺相继奔轶。聪犯高化等三州，旺轶入雷境。舜陟命将严守津岸，使不得登。聪无水可饮，而食且尽，转泊南恩，乞降于东路。旺寻亦就缚。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"eb398158cd20415e87c45fdcb621f873\");'><span id='eb398158cd20415e87c45fdcb621f873_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1138')\">1136-1138年</a>，53-55岁</div><div id='eb398158cd20415e87c45fdcb621f873' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，知静江府。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>题静江府枕流亭诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题静江府枕流亭（宋·胡舜陟）<br />　　七言绝句　押先韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->平生壮志在燕然，投老南征示息肩。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->鼷鼠发机端可笑，暂休戎马弄潺湲。<span class=\"small\">①</span><!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 以上元陈世隆《宋诗拾遗》卷一三</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年</a>，知静江府。修市马政。岁中市马二千四百匹，诏赏之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年</a>，知静江府。南丹州猺莫公晟命知南丹，桀黠不受敕，结猺人入暴省地。舜陟揭榜诸洞，募能擒斩者以其官爵赀产畀之，又益以钱盐万计，猺人动心，公晟屏迹。时以舜陟一榜，贤于兵数万。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年</a>，知静江府。转中散大夫，封绩溪开国男，食邑三百户，进中奉大夫封子爵，加邑三百户中大夫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，知静江府。奏训练土丁保丁。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏训练土丁保丁。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，尝劾秦桧十余条，桧深恨之，讽御史中丞常同奏之罢职提举洪州玉龙观。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"24e3b063b09c43dd922737dce61950de\");'><span id='24e3b063b09c43dd922737dce61950de_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1143')\">1140-1143年</a>，57-60岁</div><div id='24e3b063b09c43dd922737dce61950de' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1141')\">1140-1141年</a>，起知静江府，复为广西经略。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年4月28日</a>，诏令节制广东广西湖南三路兵骆科。平之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，进封新安伯加邑二百户，通请大夫加封金紫光禄大夫太师明国公食邑九百户。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，冬，上疏论岳飞冤。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论岳飞冤。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1142')\">1142年9月16日</a>，撰家谱序。<span class='label'>作品：</span>家谱序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1143&endYear=1143')\">1143年</a>，知静江府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1143&endYear=1143')\">1143年6月18日</a>，知邕州俞儋有赃，为运副吕源所按，事连舜陟，提举太平观。先是，舜陟与源有隙，舜陟因讨郴贼，劾源沮军事，源以书抵秦桧，讼舜陟受金盗马，非讪朝政。桧素恶舜陟，入其说，奏遣大理寺官袁楠、燕仰之往推劾，居两旬，辞不服，死狱中。舜陟再守静江有惠爱，人闻其死，皆为之哭，丐者亦敛数十钱致祭。后，夫人汪氏诉冤得白，赐葬湖州，遣官致祭。累赠少师。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.415455,"Longitude":110.332056,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN450323","Title":"灵川","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e65b17d9662946d29314aa52f10ddc10\");'><span id='e65b17d9662946d29314aa52f10ddc10_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，53岁</div><div id='e65b17d9662946d29314aa52f10ddc10' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，易灵川县滑石泉名漱玉泉，并有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>题漱玉泉诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆出版社1999（《北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊》））</span><br /></div>"}],"Title":"胡舜陟 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1083-1143)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：胡培翚等《胡少师年谱》　录入整理：彭洁明</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 5, 117.2377985, 31.6319025, 8)\">0-26岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">绩溪</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">湖州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">上饶</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(5, 9, 117.5379745, 32.41973, 8)\">26-40岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">绍兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">嘉兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(9, 15, 117.4517585, 32.5415, 8)\">40-47岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">盱眙</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">合肥</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">苏州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">杭州</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(15, 22, 115.2290675, 27.481089, 7)\">47-53岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">绩溪</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">绩溪</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">九江</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(19)\">合肥</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(20)\">广州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(21)\">桂林</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(22, 26, 115.195504, 28.089454, 7)\">53-60岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(22)\">灵川</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(23)\">桂林</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(24)\">湖州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(25)\">桂林</a></p>"}]}